name: sen·ti·men·tal
description: When I first bought this, I already had the dream of riding my child with this scooter. But the reality says. Otherwise, the pandemic made everything fall apart. I had to be able to survive. One way to stay afloat is to sell the scooter. When I sold the scooter, I apologized to my daughter because I failed to get her to ride it. That's life not everything that is planned will come true.
